name: KADOMEKADVENTURE SERIES Episode 1 – The Beginning. Part 1
description:
Special edition for the #HEN500K event

In the afternoon, I was taking a leisurely walk in a forest. Suddenly I heard a neighing sound. I then tried to find out where the sound was coming from. As the sound grew louder, I saw that there was a puppy in the distance in front of me.

I approached the puppy and when it realized my presence, it suddenly jumped up crying at me. I asked "what happened" to the puppy. Then the puppy pointed towards the bottom of the cliff. Looks like someone needs help.

Should I help him? Who is that person?
